'''天主教埃雷欣教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Ereximensis}}；{{lang-pt|Diocese de Erexim}}）是[[巴西|巴西]]一個[[天主教|天主教]][[教區|教區]]，位於東南部[[南大河州|南大河州]]北部，包括三十個市。此教區屬[[天主教帕蘇豐杜總教區|帕蘇豐杜總教區]]。

教區於1971年5月27日成立<ref>{{cite web |title=PASSOFUNDENSIS ET ALIARUM (EREXIMENSIS-CRUCIS ALTAE-RIVOGRANDENSIS)* |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/paul-vi/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_p-vi_apc_19710527_ereximensis.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2019-08-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190821175116/https://w2.vatican.va/content/paul-vi/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_p-vi_apc_19710527_ereximensis.html |archivedate=2019-08-21 |language=la |date=1971-05-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2006年時有172,000名教友，佔總人口78.9%。教區有廿八個堂區和五十位[[司鐸|司鐸]]。現任教區主教為{{link-pt|阿迪米爾·安多尼·馬扎利|Adimir Antônio Mazali}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 15.04.2020 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/04/15/200415b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2020-04-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200416100651/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2020/04/15/200415b.html |archivedate=2020-04-16 |language=en |date=2020-04-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休主教為{{link-pt|吉羅尼莫·扎南德雷阿|Girônimo Zanandréa}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 06.06.2012 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2012/06/06/0334/00786.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-08-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190821172058/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2012/06/06/0334/00786.html |archivedate=2019-08-21 |language=it |date=2012-06-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

